<p>Here's how to use Eardogger:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Install the "Mark my spot" and "Where was I" bookmarklets, and bookmark the homepage.</li>
  <li>To pause the webcomic or serial you're reading, click "Mark my spot."</li>
  <li>To resume reading from where you paused, either:
    <ul>
      <li>Use the links on the <a href="/">Eardogger homepage</a>.</li>
      <li>Go directly to the serial you were reading and click "Where was I."</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

